 187:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
 188:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \brief
 189:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  Returns the current status of the Component (Scan is completed or Scan is in
 190:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  progress).
 191:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
 192:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \details
 193:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  This function returns a status of the hardware block whether a scan is
 194:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  currently in progress or not. If the Component is busy, no new scan or setup
 195:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  widgets is made. The critical section (i.e. disable global interrupt)
 196:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  is recommended for the application when the device transitions from
 197:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  the active mode to sleep or deep sleep modes.
 198:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
 199:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \return
 200:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  Returns the current status of the Component:
 201:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *    - CapSense_NOT_BUSY - No scan is in progress and a next scan
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Bryce\AppData\Local\Temp\ccB7vQfQ.s 			page 5


 202:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *      can be initiated.
 203:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *    - CapSense_SW_STS_BUSY - The previous scanning is not completed
 204:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *      and the hardware block is busy.
 205:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
 206:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *******************************************************************************/
 207:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** uint32 CapSense_IsBusy(void)
 208:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** {
 209:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c ****     return (CapSense_dsRam.status & CapSense_SW_STS_BUSY);
 210:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** }
