2095:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2096:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \brief
2097:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  This is an internal function that calculates the LFSR scale value.
2098:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2099:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \details
2100:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  The LFSR scale value is used to increase the clock dither if the desired dither
2101:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  is wider than can be achieved with the current Sense Clock Divider and current LFSR
2102:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  period.
2103:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2104:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  This returns the LFSR scale value needed to keep the clock dither in
2105:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  range +/-10%.
2106:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2107:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \param
2108:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  snsClkDivider The divider value for the sense clock.
2109:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  lfsrSize The period of the LFSR sequence.
2110:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *          CapSense_CLK_SOURCE_DIRECT The spreadspectrum is not used.
2111:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *          CapSense_CLK_SOURCE_SSC1   The length of LFSR sequence is 63 cycles.
2112:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *          CapSense_CLK_SOURCE_SSC2   The length of LFSR sequence is 127 cycles.
2113:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *          CapSense_CLK_SOURCE_SSC3   The length of LFSR sequence is 255 cycles.
2114:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *          CapSense_CLK_SOURCE_SSC4   The length of LFSR sequence is 511 cycles.
2115:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2116:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \return The LFSR scale value needed to keep the clock dither in range +/-10%.
2117:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2118:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *******************************************************************************/
